What's new in this version

• Pause now runs quietly with no persistent notification on Android 13+.
• Simpler setup: one detection method (Usage access) — works alongside your banking and finance apps.
• Clear, plain-English explanation of exactly what Pause reads (only the app name + time) and what it can't (your screen, messages, keystrokes). Nothing leaves your phone.
• The reminder no longer pops up over a locked or off screen, and your scroll time counts even if an app was already open.
